{"tid":1390412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳] 抗爭=有糖派，有風打，有錢收：民建聯倡派糖，葉劉建議派錢","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:06:59.000Z","uid":173849,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"794b672c2aab37167253c637e329b444adf635be","tid":1390412,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"民建聯倡政府「派糖」 免公屋租金兩月 撥4億元滅蟲鼠 (23:08)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190730/s00001/1564498184676/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E3%80%8C%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%96%E3%80%8D-%E5%85%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%88-%E6%92%A54%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E6%BB%85%E8%9F%B2%E9%BC%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190730%2Fs00001%2F1564498184676%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25B3%2596%25E3%2580%258D-%25E5%2585%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%259C%2588-%25E6%2592%25A54%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25BB%2585%25E8%259F%25B2%25E9%25BC%25A0&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=29c3b5d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190730%2Fs00001%2F1564498184676%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25B3%2596%25E3%2580%258D-%25E5%2585%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%259C%2588-%25E6%2592%25A54%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25BB%2585%25E8%259F%25B2%25E9%25BC%25A0&h=cdcde814\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190730/s00001/1564498184676/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E3%80%8C%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%96%E3%80%8D-%E5%85%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%88-%E6%92%A54%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E6%BB%85%E8%9F%B2%E9%BC%A0</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯成員今日（30日）與財政司長陳茂波見面，預計經濟惡劣情況仍會持續，民建聯提出，特區政府有必要在短期內推出一次過的紓困措施，以安民心。民建聯提出11項「派糖」及民生措施建議，包括寬免公屋租金兩個月、撥4億元予區議會用作處理蟲鼠治理問題。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯提出的建議包括：<br />\n1. 發放額外一個月高齡津貼、長者生活津貼、傷殘津貼金額、綜援、低收入在職家庭津貼等社會福利資助；<br />\n2. 全港幼稚園及中、小學生一次過發放2500元開學津貼；<br />\n3. 寬免公屋租金兩個月；<br />\n4. 為合資格領取長者醫療券的長者額外再提供一次過1000元金額；<br />\n5. 寬免2019／20年度全年差餉，由預算案提出的以每戶每季1500元為上限，增至2500元<span style=\"color: red;\">（益業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span>；<br />\n6. 增加本年度寬免薪俸稅及利得稅限額，由預算案建議的75%，增加至100%，上限維持20,000元；<br />\n7. 每戶住宅用電補貼2000元、用水補貼1000元；<br />\n8. 豁免商業的相關牌照費用，包括「商業登記證」、「販商牌照」、「船隻牌照」、「魚排牌照」等<span style=\"color: red;\">（益商家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span>；<br />\n9. 為全港新鮮豬肉零售檔戶提供每月2000元為期半年的特別資助，並寛免公眾街市出售鮮肉攤檔的租金三個月，以及全港出售鮮肉的新鮮糧食店牌照的費用一年；<br />\n10. 把「樓宇更新大行動2.0」的支援對象由50年或以上舊樓業主，擴展至30年或以上的舊樓業主<span style=\"color: red;\">（又益業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span>；<br />\n11. <span style=\"color: red;\">設立由區議會主導的4億元基金，積極改善社區內的蟲鼠治理問題</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨會見陳茂波建議派8000元  葉劉：政府應與市民同行<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/355168/%E6%96%B0%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%8B%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%B4%BE8000%E5%85%83-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%89%E8%88%87%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F355168%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25B4%25BE8000%25E5%2585%2583-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25A1%258C&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=27ff8a40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/355168/%E6%96%B0%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E6%9C%83%E8%A6%8B%E9%99%B3%E8%8C%82%E6%B3%A2%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%B4%BE8000%E5%85%83-%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%89%E8%88%87%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n請各位多多宣傳，對深藍廢老好有用<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">愈抗爭，著數愈多</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9816b57423c9243b9d98fa7ccd4612c3633c026","tid":1390412,"uid":173849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"罷工不能，請屌建制<br />\n<br />\n［文宣唔該］罷工冇人理？屌港豬之餘，唔該望下工聯會騎劫左幾多個工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ff49597ddd23d88742f0c5e234daebe7598c32d","tid":1390412,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"ea2302cdbf07599f77c7278b6373524e81c5935e","tid":1390412,"uid":166838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c31b15d64488b09f019fc69434a7c9789eaae3a9","tid":1390412,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"依住先！"},{"pid":"47294e95f9b0cc018c037d4977d72ea0603af27a","tid":1390412,"uid":279401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31b15d64488b09f019fc69434a7c9789eaae3a9","tid":1390412,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"依住先！"},"cite